      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A ceremonial welcome was given for India's latest gift to the people of Sri Lanka in the presence of President Ranil Wickremesinghe and other dignitaries. The Dornier 228 aircraft was delivered to the Sri Lanka Air Force (SLAF) and will increase security. Pix by Kithsiri de Mel"
